<p><strong>Proof 1: </strong></p>
<p><span>Even many Muslim Translators didn't accept this falsehood and translated it correctly (i.e. they used the word 'desire' instead of 'recitation'). </span><span>We invite people to go this </span><a rpl="" class="relative pointer-events-auto a
  
  
  
  
