<p><strong>Proof 3</strong>: </p>
<p>All 50 traditions about the incident of Satanic Verses are unanimously telling that the prophet indeed got mislead due to his 'desire'. How can you neglect all these traditions, and then change the meaning of (<b><i>tamannā</i></b> تمنی) only based upon your conjecture? </p>
<p><strong>Proof 4</strong>:</p>
